                  II-VI group colloidal quantum dots/ block copolymer nanocomposites、Clay / polymer nanocomposites, Polyhedral Oligomeric Silsesquioxane/polyimide nanocomposites、Synthesis of donor-acceptor conjugated polymers for photovoltaics、Conjugated polymers/nanoparticles for light emitting diode and photovoltaic devices




                
























